# A native Gnuplot wrapper library for Open Object Rexx.

package gnuplot
version 0.1.0

summary A native Gnuplot wrapper library for Open Object Rexx.

description """
A native wrapper library for interacting with Gnuplot from Open Object Rexx. It allows to easily generate plots, export graphics to several image formats or run real-time interactive sessions. Cross-platform support for Windows and POSIX operating systems.
"""

license Apache-2.0
author Salvador Parra Camacho
homepage https://github.com/sparrac/oorexx-gnuplot

require oorexx >= 5.0
